00:43:37.812 --> 00:43:44.610
and then when I integrate over
that, well the moment the atom

00:43:44.610 --> 00:43:47.040
makes a transition
there is no longer

00:43:47.040 --> 00:43:48.670
any correlation
between the force.

00:43:48.670 --> 00:43:53.630
Everything becomes random and
the integral averages out to 0.

00:43:53.630 --> 00:43:55.180
So in other words,
that's the way

00:43:55.180 --> 00:43:56.770
how you should look
