00:44:13.980 --> 00:44:16.000
randomizes the system.

00:44:16.000 --> 00:44:22.330
So therefore, this integral
over the correlation function

00:44:22.330 --> 00:44:26.740
is nothing else then the force
squared times the typical time

00:44:26.740 --> 00:44:29.850
scale for a transition.

00:44:29.850 --> 00:44:33.630
So if you put that
in on resonance,

00:44:33.630 --> 00:44:36.470
